### 会員登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "name": "テストユーザー",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}
### ログイン成功
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "password": "password"
}
### ログイン失敗
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "password": "abc"
}
### 所持グッズ登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goods
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "goodsName": "〇〇 キーホルダー",
  "description": "ライブ会場限定",
  "imageUrl": ""
}

### 所持グッズ一覧
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goods

### 所持グッズ削除
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/goods/1

### 交換希望登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wanted
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "goodsName": "◯◯ トレーディングカード",
  "conditions": "目立つ傷や折れがないものを希望"
}

### 交換希望一覧
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wanted

### 交換希望削除
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/wanted/1